    • setMatchResult

      public MoneyManagementRecipientVerificationsParams.Builder setMatchResult(MoneyManagementRecipientVerificationsParams.MatchResult matchResult)
      Required. Expected match level of the RecipientVerification to be created: match, close_match, no_match, unavailable. For close_match, the simulated response appends "close_match" to the provided name in match_result_details.matched_name.

    • setRecipient

      public MoneyManagementRecipientVerificationsParams.Builder setRecipient(String recipient)
      ID of the recipient account. Required if the recipient distinct from the sender. Leave empty if the recipient and sender are the same entity (i.e. for me-to-me payouts).
